  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |=
|15|u=u|d=d|l=l|r=r}}<small><center>рис.1. Пятёрки</center></small></div>
{{столбец}}
<div style="clear:both; padding: 2px; border-width: 0; margin:5px;">
{{Goban 15x15|=
